<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ wǒ men qiú nǐ 迦南798</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ men qiú nǐ, zhǔ wǒ men qiú nǐ, chà pài gōng rén dào liè guó qù.
 zhǔ wǒ men qiú nǐ, zhǔ wǒ men qiú nǐ, chà pài gōng rén dào liè guó qù.
 nà lǐ de tǔ de běn shì nǐ de. nà lǐ de mín zú zhèng xū yào nǐ.
 wǒ men yào chuán yáng nǐ, liè guó yào guī shùn nǐ. nǐ de míng zài quán de yǐ bèi gāo jǔ.
 nǐ de míng zài quán de yǐ bèi gāo jǔ.</lyrics>
